          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN",
                "MWPC",
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  Separate  periods  of  beam   time",
                " have been devoted  to  the  different  parts  of  the",
                " experiment using the CATS alone, CATS/TRAJAN and COPP",
                " arangements.",
                "The compton  and two photon spectrometer CATS consists",
                " of the Mainz 48 cm diameter x 64 cm  modular  Nai(Tl)",
                " spectrometer in  combination  with  2-pi  array of 61",
                " BaF-2 crystals at the opposite side of the target.",
                "Gottingen trajectory  analyser  TRAJAN consists of two",
                " hodoscopes, a wire chamber in  distance  of  54.8  cm",
                " from the center of scattering target, a plastic strip",
                " detector in a distance of 207.5 cm,  and  a  wall  of",
                " NaI(Tl) crystal in a distance of 222.5 cm.",
                "Genova/Frascatti coincidence photon proton arrangement",
                " COPP consists  of  12  photon-proton  detector  pairs",
                " where proton detectors are plastic  scintillator  and",
                " the photon   detectors   are   lead-glass  detectots.",
                " Each detector is  furnished  with  a  collimator  and",
                " plastic-scintillator de  detector serving as veto and",
                " coincidence detectors respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Direct measurement of differential cross section."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "   Statistical   errors   are   given.   The",
                " systematic errors  are  4.4  %  below  350  MeV,  6 %",
                " between 350 and 380 MeV, and 8 % above."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Differential  cross sections for Compton scattering by",
                " the proton have been measured in the energy  interval",
                " between 200   and   500   MeV  at  acattering  angles",
                " theta-cms =  75  degree and 90 degree using the CATS,",
                " the CATS/TRAJAN, and the COPP setups with the Glasgow",
                " Tagger at MAMI (Mainz)."
              ]
            }
          ],
